<div class="container">
  <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 d-flex justify-content-center">
      <div class="my-2 pt-5 home-text mx-auto">
        <h1 class="main-header mb-5">Gimme a Song</h1>
        <p>Feeling stuck?</p>
        <p>Not sure what kind of song to write?</p>
        <p>Click <strong>New Idea</strong> to generate a new songwriting challenge.</p>
        <p>Click <strong>Gimme a Song</strong> to randomly change everything.</p>
        <p>When you are happy with your song idea, click <strong>Done</strong>.</p>
        <div class="text-center gap-2">
          <%= link_to 'New Idea', new_song_path, class: "btn main-btn btn-lg my-2" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="image col-12 col-lg-6">
      <%= image_tag 'demo.gif', class: "demo-gif mt-5", alt: "demo of website" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
